flowchart TB
    subgraph VPC[VPC]
        subgraph AZA[Availability Zone A]
            SubnetA[Private Isolated Subnet A]
        end

        subgraph AZB[Availability Zone B]
            SubnetB[Private Isolated Subnet B]
        end

        Lambda[Lambda ENIs]
        Migration[ECS Migration Task]
        Proxy[RDS Proxy]
        Aurora[Aurora PostgreSQL]

        Lambda --> Proxy
        Migration --> Proxy
        Proxy --> Aurora

        Lambda -.-> SubnetA
        Lambda -.-> SubnetB
        Migration -.-> SubnetA
        Migration -.-> SubnetB
        Proxy -.-> SubnetA
        Proxy -.-> SubnetB
        Aurora -.-> SubnetA
        Aurora -.-> SubnetB
    end

    Client[Client] --> Api[API Gateway HTTP API]
    Api --> Lambda

